                "invention-title": [
                    "Device for promoting dispersion and cracking of methane in melt through mechanical shearing and method for preparing high-value carbon material and hydrogen",
                    "一种机械剪切促进熔体中甲烷分散及裂解的装置及其制备高值碳材料及氢气的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a device for promoting dispersion and cracking of methane in a melt through mechanical shearing and a method for preparing a high-value carbon material and hydrogen through the device, and belongs to the technical field of new energy materials. The device comprises a reaction chamber, a mechanical shear gas dispersion mechanism, a breather pipe and a heating mechanism, the heating mechanism is arranged outside the reaction chamber; an air inlet of the breather pipe is arranged above the reaction chamber; the bottom of the mechanical shear gas dispersion mechanism is arranged in the reaction chamber; the mechanical shearing gas dispersing mechanism comprises a motor, a coupler, a transmission shaft and a shearing rotating head which are connected in sequence; a stator is arranged outside the shearing rotating head and the transmission shaft; a hole is formed in the overlapped part of the lower end of the stator and the shearing rotor; and the shearing rotating head is positioned above the air outlet of the breather pipe. The invention also provides a method for preparing the high-value carbon material and hydrogen by using the device. The device for promoting dispersion and cracking of methane in the melt through mechanical shearing is easy to operate, the production efficiency of carbon products and hydrogen is high, and the prepared carbon products are high in quality."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种机械剪切促进熔体中甲烷分散及裂解的装置及其制备高值碳材料及氢气的方法，属于新能源材料技术领域。该装置包括反应室、机械剪切气体分散机构、通气管及加热机构；加热机构设置于反应室外部；通气管的进气口设置于反应室上方；机械剪切气体分散机构的底部设置于反应室内部；机械剪切气体分散机构包括依次连接的电机、联轴器、传动轴及剪切转头；剪切转头和传动轴外部设置有定子；定子的下端与剪切转头重合部分设置有孔；剪切转头位于通气管的出气口上方。本发明还提供用上述装置制备高值碳材料及氢气的方法。本发明的机械剪切促进熔体中甲烷分散及裂解的装置操作简单，碳产物及氢气的生产效率高，制备的碳产物品质高。"
                }
